Class FluidBase

java.lang.Object
org.moddingx.libx.base.FluidBase
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.minecraft.world.level.ItemLike, Registerable
public class FluidBase extends Object implements Registerable, net.minecraft.world.level.ItemLike
A Registerable that registers a fluid, a flowing fluid, a liquid block and a bucket item.
